project_descr:
The Construction of  Sewage Treatment Plant and Mian Pressure Line in Khan Younis in the Gaza Strip . 
The project aims at protecting the public health and improving the environmental conditions of Khan Younis residents.

outputs.output_descr: Khan Younis Waste Water Treatment Plant (KY WWTP) is a strategic environmental project aims at protecting public health, water resources and environment of more than 320,000 residents of Khan Younis Governorate in the Gaza Strip.
